 majority of our customers prefer to buy and hold.=C2=A0</p></blockquote><p=
 style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Fine sure yes most customers buy and hold, but m=
ost of the=C2=A0<em>money=C2=A0</em>comes from customers YOLOing options.</=
